node_modules/
dist/
.angular/
*.log

# Editor/preview artifacts not used at runtime
**/src/assets/preview/

# Duplicate/unused image webps (apps use .jpg in assets/images)
**/src/assets/images/*.webp

# README screenshots — hosted at https://cloudgate.dev/assets/app-templates/
**/docs/screenshots/

# Capacitor native shells — regenerate with `npx cap add android|ios`
**/android/
**/ios/

# Per-workspace Cloudgate editor artifacts (see each folder's .cloudgate/.gitignore)
**/.cloudgate/*
!**/.cloudgate/.gitignore
